@startuml
title UC09 - Consultar Extrato da Conta

hide footbox
autoactivate off
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #374151
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #9CA3AF
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F5FF
skinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceDatabaseBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceDatabaseBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
skinparam sequenceBoundaryBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceBoundaryBackgroundColor #ECFEFF
skinparam sequenceControlBorderColor #374151
skinparam sequenceControlBackgroundColor #F0F9FF
skinparam sequenceActivationBorderColor #111827
skinparam sequenceActivationBackgroundColor #CFE3FF
skinparam ParticipantPadding 35
skinparam BoxPadding 12
skinparam maxMessageSize 90

actor Aluno as A
boundary "Perfil do Aluno\nNext.js" as Front
control "AlunoController\nMicronaut" as AlunoCtrl
control "TransacaoController\nMicronaut" as TransCtrl
control "TransacaoRepository" as TransRepo
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

A -> Front: Acessa perfil do aluno
activate Front

Front -> AlunoCtrl: GET /alunos/{id}
activate AlunoCtrl

AlunoCtrl -> DB: SELECT aluno WHERE id = ?
activate DB

DB --> AlunoCtrl: Dados do aluno
deactivate DB

AlunoCtrl --> Front: AlunoResponse
deactivate AlunoCtrl

Front -> TransCtrl: GET /transacoes/aluno/{id}
activate TransCtrl

TransCtrl -> TransRepo: findByDestinatarioId(alunoId)
activate TransRepo

TransRepo -> DB: SELECT transacoes recebidas
activate DB

DB --> TransRepo: Lista de transacoes
deactivate DB

TransRepo --> TransCtrl: List<Transacao>
deactivate TransRepo

TransCtrl --> Front: ExtratoResponse[]
deactivate TransCtrl

Front -> Front: Renderiza saldo e historico
Front --> A: Exibe extrato da conta
deactivate Front

@enduml
